<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_385" id="192r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_385_r1l12"><expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vom Eglofſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_385_r1l13"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Conrad vihofers vvegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l14">Laſſen vvir ew vviſſen / daʒ Er cʒu dercʒeit niht anheim ıſt / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l15">vvenn der herheim kümpt / So vvöllen wir Jn beſenden vnd cʒurede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l16">ſecʒen vnd ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ein <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wiſʒen laſſen ob dıe <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l17">ewren vvegen an vns vordert <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Andr<ex>ee</ex></expan> A xj<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_385" id="192r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vom Eglofstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Conrad Vihofers wegen,
                        lassen wir ew wissen, daz er czu derczeit niht anheim ist, und wenn der
                        herheim kümpt, so wöllen wir in besenden und czu rede seczen und ew
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        wiszen lassen, ob die <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> von ewren wegen an
                        uns vordert. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Andr<ex>ee</ex></expan> <expan>a<ex>nno</ex></expan> xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
